description:
Returning special guest Steve Shives buckles his seatbelt and goes for a ride in the space trailer this week, and it was a wild time! Tune in for a discussion of the latest goings-on in the Exposition Quadrant, wherein Picard mixes it up with some pissed off Romulans; the crew of La Sirena add a new member to their ragtag group of losers; and we finally see a beloved, well-missed face.
